data.description:
**PRICE REDUCTION - MOVE-IN READY!!!**

***SELLER OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS RATE BUY DOWN OR CLOSING COSTS WITH FULL PRICE OFFER***

READY TO MOVE IN - NEW FLOORING AND FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT.  Lovely three-bedroom and two-bath home with an open floor plan is just minutes from 35 and many dining and shopping options. Neutral colors and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. Perfect home for the first-time buyer or investment property. Strong rental history. Large backyard with new fence and covered patio. Convenient access to school, shopping, dining, I-820 and I-35W.
